name: (Concept) Torture Rack/Operating Table
description:
Do you like torture ? No ? Wel..........

Do you like bondage then ? No ? Well.................

Do you like hospitals or laboratories ? No ? Well......................................

Well, You have a perfectly safe brain. But this Lora allows you to strap girls on an operating table or a wooden torture rack, so you can make a mad scientist scenario.

Recommended prompts : torturerack, operating table, wooden table, straps, strapped, lying

Recommended 0.8, but 1 is fine too.

Shoul;d work with several models.
